rComments: Great prof. Great course. Recommend it.
Very interesting Prof. Answers questions clearly, responds to emails promptly and takes the time to explain things in detail.
Great Prof. keeps students engaged even during the particular low points of the course. Will definitely consider taking his class later on.
Really good professor. Student attendance rate was ~100%! Very good slides (don't need text). Would take his grad courses if I ever do a Masters.
Simply the best.  Clear, funny, helpful and organized.  His lecture slides are great and he makes sure that you understand the material.  Nothing else can be said, Greg Steffan rocks!

Great prof, very friendly, clear, and makes an excellent effort to answer any questions.  Gives short talks about labs to help prepare, and ensure you know everything you need to before going into a lab.
Excellent Prof., even though the course could be a little bit "tricky".

Excellent Proff. Keeps you engaged in every class. One of the few proffs who tries to keep the students involved as he lectures and the best thing about him is from lecture to lecture he will squeeze in a lot of material but you wont even feel it.
There's no need to read the textbook! Just go to lectures! Lectures were fun. He tries his best not to confuuuuzzzze people. Knows his stuff.
